---
title: Sugar Shack Maple Sausage Breakfast Bake Serves 2 | with Buttered Panko Crust
description: Crack through the crisp panko crust to reveal fluffy egg strata stuffed full of sausage, onions and pepper! It's a dish that comes dressed to impress.
